<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2017-02-28</DATELINE><TITLE>Novel 1-[5-(4-bromophenoxy)pentyl]-3-(2-arylamino- 2-oxoethyl)uracils and their antiviral properties</TITLE><BODY>The title compounds were prepared from 1-[5-(4-bromophenoxy) pentyl]uracil by the introduction of N-arylacetamide moiety at the 3-position, the better approach involving the use of N-aryl-2-chloroacetamides as the reactants. Antiviral activity of the obtained compounds was estimated.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>